Pokemon: The species name. Form goes in (parentheses).
Rarity: Spawn chance, in order Common > Uncommon > Rare > Legendary > Mythical
Starter: Whether it's a Grass/Fire/Water trio starter, a Pikaclone starter, or a Special starter.
Second Type: Some Pokemon have an extra type.
Egg Group 1: Only Pokemon with the same egg group can offspring.
Egg Group 2: Some Pokemon have two egg groups.
Second Ability: The Ability unlocked when joining a team.
Hidden Ability: The ability unlocked by Hidden Training.
Height (ft in): Average height in Feet and Inches.
♂/♀ Ratio: Gender spawn ratio, 0 is male only, 1 is female only.
Description: Pokedex style description of the Pokemon's average appearance, behavior, and powers. This is not a Pokemon. This is a template for creating other Pokemon. Think of it like an Egg, that contains the entry you're writing.
